channel.description:
# G! Turbo! - Wazza Edition
### Due to not enough classes yet. The thread for GI turbo is not yet being used. [Grand Idea FoL - Turbo Edition ](https://forum.imperium42.com/t/grand-idea-fol-turbo-edition/75468/11).
# Average Rules.
* Game starts at [date=2019-03-16 time=21:00:00 timezone="Europe/London"] * Days are 15 minutes. Twilight is 2 minutes. Nights are 5 minutes, unless I’m a failure and extend it. * Early day actions will be processed during the day, late day actions will be processed during Twilight, due to me being a failure once more. * There can be more than one King, but only a King election will take place once there are no Kings remaining. * I’m on PC, so don’t have mercy, feel free to make me want to die. * The amount of players are infinite but there must be at least 7 players.
1. GamerPoke 2. Meteoro 4. Margaret 5. Priestess 6. Isaac 8. Mercenary 9. Hjasik 10. Luna
# There is no line for classes until the game begins.
Classes will be watered down if they are not able to be used in Turbo, if classes can not work in turbo situations like this, they will be re-rolled.

item.title: GI Turbo - Game End - Mercenary, Mercenary, The Mercenary, and the King allied with Mercenary wins!
item.dc:creator: Mercenary
item.description:
A young man asked, "Grandpa, how did you live before?

  • Without technology
  • No airplanes
  • Without Internet
  • Without computers
  • No Plasma or Led TVs
  • No air conditioners
  • Without cars
  • No cell phones, tablets, notebook and laptop"

Grandpa replied:

“As your generation lives today:
Without prayer,
Without compassion,
Without honor,
Without respect,
Shameless,
Without effort,
Without responsibilities,
Without modesty”

We, the people born in the last century, are blessed.

Our life is living proof.
While we play and ride a bike, we never wear helmets.
After school, we played until dusk in the neighborhood without fear.
We play with real friends, not with friends on the internet.
If we were thirsty, we drank water from the hose, not bottled.
There was no danger of sharing the same glass of juice with four friends.
We do not gain weight by eating fast food.
There was also nothing wrong with walking barefoot.
We never use a supplement to stay healthy.
We used to create our own toys and play with them.
Our parents were not rich. They gave love, not material things.
We do not own phones, cell phones, DVDs, Play Station, Xbox, video games, personal computers, internet, WhatsApp, we had real friends.
We visited the home of our friends without being invited and enjoyed the meal with them.
Family members lived nearby to enjoy family time.
We may be in black and white photos, but you can find colorful memories in these photos.
We are a unique and more understanding generation because we are the last generation to have heard their parents, grandparents and uncles. We also respect parents, teachers, older people, and even the church priest.

We are a LIMITED edition! We are less every day. Enjoy while you can.
Learn with us.
And keep in mind that, it took us a lot of work to build this country that is being destroyed today!

Read full topic
